# Version History

The ARAF standard is actively maintained. Version history is published here to provide transparency about how the framework has evolved, to allow institutional audiences to identify the version against which an assessment was conducted, and to signal that the standard will continue to evolve as autonomous system governance practice develops.

Assessments conducted under earlier versions remain valid for the period of their certification. Reassessments are conducted against the current version at the time of reassessment.

